;" }{MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}{PARA 202 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 3 "od:" }
{MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 204 "" 0 "" {TEXT 208 15 "here it is
